&lt;li&gt;Creating an Inclusive Course Climate, 9/11&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Backward Design and Learning Objectives, 9/18&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active Learning, 9/25&lt;/li&gt;
