&lt;h2&gt;Ways to Be More Inclusive in Your Course&amp;nbsp;(for Faculty)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A 60-minute workshop for Columbia Faculty.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;How do I create a community in which all students feel a sense of belonging? How can I partner with my students to co-create the learning environment?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
