&lt;p&gt;Welcome to office hours for graduate student instructors! Gather with your fellow teachers and the friendly CTL team to discuss what&amp;rsquo;s going on in your classroom this semester and make a plan for the future.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this session, we&amp;rsquo;ll reflect on teaching experiences so far and chat&amp;nbsp;about crafting a sustainable teaching practice by exploring questions like:&amp;nbsp;Are you giving efficient and effective feedback? How much time are you spending preparing for class sessions? Can you and your students keep up? Inclusive teaching is sustainable teaching!&lt;/p&gt;
